entry.def: Pinball is a game in which a player presses two buttons on each side of a pinball machine in order to hit a small ball to the top of the machine. The aim of the game is to prevent the ball reaching the bottom of the machine by pressing the buttons.

means.word_mean: 1. a game played on a sloping board; the object is to propel marbles against pins or into pockets
